parameters.name: $src_ACX_questionreply$
parameters.label: DBConnection_SRCM
parameters.customQuery:
SELECT distinct q.CMMContainer as cmm_container,
 DisplayDesc as display_desc,
 Id as id,
 Name as name,
 ParentId as parent_id,
 RowId as row_id,
 q.SystemId as system_id,
 Text as text,
 Value as value,
 VisibleInd as visible_ind
from questionreply q
join advrxxchangedbeans a
on q.CMMContainer = a.CMMContainer
and q.SystemId = a.SystemId
where q.Name in (
  '03PreviousCarrierPropertyLimitsPremium','AnnualRevenue','AnnualRevenueFour','AnnualRevenueThree','AnnualRevenueTwo',
  'AnyLapse','AnyLapsePast','AnyOutbuildings','ArsonConvicted','BreedDescription','BreedDetails','BusinessDescOffPremise',
  'BusinessDescOffPremiseFour','BusinessDescOffPremiseThree','BusinessDescOffPremiseTwo','BusinessDescOnPremise',
  'BusinessDescOnPremiseFour','BusinessDescOnPremiseThree','BusinessDescOnPremiseTwo','BusinessDescOther','BusinessDescOtherFour',
  'BusinessDescOtherThree','BusinessDescOtherTwo','BusinessType','BusinessTypeFour','BusinessTypeThree','BusinessTypeTwo',
  'CancelledRecently','ClaimsRecently','ConstructionOrRenovation','DateAndReason','DayCareCount','DayCareCountFour',
  'DayCareCountThree',  'DayCareCountTwo','DayCareOnPremises','DayCarePremises','DiscussedWithUnderwriter','DogsCare',
  'DwellingVacantReason','DwellingVisible','ElectricalService','EstimatedCompletionDate','FencedWithGate','FireApparatus',
  'FrameDwellings','FruitsAndVeg','FruitsAndVegFour','FruitsAndVegThree','FruitsAndVegTwo','FullFoundation','HoovedAnimals',
  'HoovedAnimalsFour','HoovedAnimalsThree','HoovedAnimalsTwo','IsolatedProperty','lapseDescription','LicensedDayCare',
  'LicensedDayCareFour','LicensedDayCareThree','LicensedDayCareTwo','LocationAddress','LocationAddressFour','LocationAddressThree',
  'LocationAddressTwo','LocationOfBusiness','LocationOfDayCare','LockingGate','Measurements','NumberOfBusiness','OilHeated',
  'OnlineHome','OtherInsurance','PolicyNum','PoolOnPremises','PrevDiscussed','PrevKnown','PrimaryHeat','PriorCarrier',
  'PurchasePrice','RelationshipDescription','RemovableLadder','RiskCarrierName','RiskNumber10PriorCarrier',
  'RiskNumber11PriorCarrier','RiskNumber12PriorCarrier','RiskNumber13PriorCarrier','RiskNumber14PriorCarrier',
  'RiskNumber15PriorCarrier','RiskNumber16PriorCarrier','RiskNumber17PriorCarrier','RiskNumber18PriorCarrier',
  'RiskNumber1PriorCarrier','RiskNumber2PriorCarrier','RiskNumber3PriorCarrier','RiskNumber4PriorCarrier','RiskNumber5PriorCarrier',
  'RiskNumber6PriorCarrier','RiskNumber7PriorCarrier','RiskNumber8PriorCarrier','RiskNumber9PriorCarrier','RiskPriorCarrier',
  'SafetyNet','SafetyNetting','SeasonalHome','SolarPanels','StoveInspection','StoveOnPremises','TankLocation','TrampolineOnPremises',
  'TrampolinePremises','UndergraduateStudents','UnderwriterDetails','UnderwritingGuidelines','UseAndOccupancy','VacantOrOccupied',
  'WiringInUse'
  ) 
  AND concat(a.adddt,' ',a.addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and concat(a.adddt,' ',a.addtm) <='$$m_Enddt'
